CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 4, 1966, pg. 4B reads: "50th Anniversary - Denorah Grand Chapter, Order of Eastern Star, celebrated its 50th Anniversary at a banquet May 20, at Taylor's Restaurant on Route 30. Among the distinguished guests was Mrs. Pattee Miller of Reading, Grand Matron of the chapter. (Harris Photo)"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and men of the Denorah Grand Chapter, Order of Eastern Star, posed behind head banquet table for fiftieth anniversary in Taylor's Restaurant, Westmoreland County
